COPY config/site.docker.yml /app/config/site.yml

COPY script /app/script/

COPY vendor /app/vendor/

COPY Rakefile /app/

COPY app /app/app/
COPY db /app/db/

ENTRYPOINT ["/app/docker-entrypoint.sh"]
